<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ف س ا:</span> <span class="c2">(فَسَا)</span> مِنْ بَابِ عَدَا وَالِاسْمُ <span class="c2">(الْفُسَاءُ)</span> بِالْمَدِّ. وَ <span class="c2">(الْفَسُوُّ)</span> عَلَى فَعُولٍ الْكَثِيرُ <span class="c2">(الْفَسْوِ)</span> .<span class="c5"> وَفِي الْمَثَلِ:</span> مَا أَقْرَبَ مَحْسَاهُ مِنْ <span class="c2">(مَفْسَاهُ)</span> .<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>